rows.label: bf11380100_0010
rows.name: Hey, everyone!

rows.label: bf11380100_0020
rows.name: Adel-sama?

rows.label: bf11380100_0030
rows.name: Adel-sama is back!

rows.label: bf11380100_0040
rows.name: Welcome back, Adel-sama!

rows.label: bf11380100_0050
rows.name:
Wow, Adel... the resistance
fighters really love you.

rows.label: bf11380100_0060
rows.name:
Originally, it was because of his popularity
that they rose up in the first place.

rows.label: bf11380100_0070
rows.name:
Speaking of which, Adel was the one who
told everyone to gather here, wasn't he?

rows.label: bf11380100_0080
rows.name: What's so special about this place?

rows.label: bf11380100_0090
rows.name: This land is Adel's domain.

rows.label: bf11380100_0100
rows.name: See? That's his manor over there.

rows.label: bf11380100_0110
rows.name:
Wow. Just what you'd expect
from an Iiran prince.

rows.label: bf11380100_0120
rows.name: It's not that big, though.

rows.label: bf11380100_0125
rows.name: And it's in such a remote area...

rows.label: bf11380100_0130
rows.name:
Do you have to be sarcastic
about everything?

rows.label: bf11380100_0140
rows.name: Oh, pardon me. I just can't help myself.

rows.label: bf11380100_0150
rows.name:
Yes, it's true this is a
frontier far from the capital.

rows.label: bf11380100_0160
rows.name: He was simply too popular.

rows.label: bf11380100_0170
rows.name:
Even though he's fourth in line to the throne,
he's loved by both the citizens and the army...

rows.label: bf11380100_0180
rows.name:
I've heard that Prince Zettar, the King's younger
brother, keeps him at a distance because of it.

rows.label: bf11380100_0190
rows.name:
I get it... I guess being
a prince is tough, too.
